      <title>比特币的暴跌引发了看涨押注的“一连串清算”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bitcoin-declines-as-the-liquidation-of-bullish-bets-accelerate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币一度出现一个多月来的最大跌幅，引发了一系列投机性加密货币头寸的清算，导致 Solana、Cardano 和 Polkadot 等规模较小的数字资产暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bitcoin-declines-as-the-liquidation-of-bullish-bets-accelerate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 19:09:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴货币因规避风险而逐步逼近 2024 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/emerging-market-currencies-hit-two-month-low-on-flight-from-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币连续第三个交易日下跌，几乎触及今年以来的新低，股市录得自 1 月份以来最大单周跌幅，因美国利率前景发生转变，地缘政治紧张局势加剧引发避险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/emerging-market-currencies-hit-two-month-low-on-flight-from-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:42:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争不安情绪加剧，股市受到打击，市场纷纷涌向债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[地缘政治风险的爆发扰乱了金融世界，导致股市下跌——同时刺激资金流向债券和美元等市场最安全的角落。石油上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 22:29:55 GMT</pubDate>
